description.en:
Bitcoin Flash Cash a solid currency and now faster than all the previous ones, fulfilling Bitcoin's original promise as ""Peer-to-Peer Electronic Money"". Users and merchants benefit from incredibly fast transactions, with fees from $ 0.001 per transaction and reliable confirmations. The future is bright with unrestricted growth, global adoption, permissionless innovation and decentralized development.

All Bitcoin bearers are welcome to join the Bitcoin Flash Cash community as we move forward in creating a solid currency, faster than all, with incredibly low fees and accessible to everyone.
